data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 4-bed, 4-bath Rambler is filled with endless possibilities. The main level boasts 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an indoor grill in the kitchen and a cozy fireplace in the living room. The lower level offers a large family room, an additional fireplace, a generous bedroom, and an updated bathroom with heated flooring and a luxurious walk-in shower. Located in a sought-after school district, this home ensures an excellent education. Features include new Anderson Windows, 3rd car parking, maintenance-free siding and fence, in-ground sprinklers, ample storage, and a private lot with a heated in-ground pool that was updated with a new liner and new equipment in 2019 and it comes with an automatic electric cover! Louvered closets and timeless built-ins add elegance. Don't miss out on this gem! Schedule a showing today and experience the true essence of this remarkable home!
